  <brief_title>Biological Markers Predicting Exercise Capacity in CF-LVAD Patients.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Biological Markers Predicting Exercise Capacity in Heart Failure Patients Supported With a Continuous-flow Left Ventricular Assist Device.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
