    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Establishing the association between biological markers and exercise capacity in
      continuous-flow left ventricular assist device patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to investigate if specific biological markers can predict exercise
      capacity in advanced heart failure patients supported with continuous-flow left ventricular
      assist device patients.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
